title: "90% vs 10%": Yogi Adityanath's New Math For Poll-Bound UP - NDTV
content: "90% vs 10%": Yogi Adityanath's New Math For Poll-Bound UP  NDTVView Full coverage on Google News
description: Claiming that the BJP was heading to a landslide victory in Uttar Pradesh assembly polls, Chief Minister Yogi Adityanath on Saturday said that the electoral contest now will be "90 percent versus 10 percent" in favour of his party.
